text: Euskadi is Basque language for the Basque Country, an autonomous community in northern Spain. Euskadi or Euzkadi may also refer to: * Euzkadi (newspaper), a Basque nationalist newspaper 1913–1939 * Euskadi (Continental cycling team), a former Spanish cycling team * Euskadi–Murias, a former Spanish cycling team * C.D. Euzkadi, a former Mexican football team ==See also== * * * ETA (separatist group) (Euskadi Ta Askatasuna, 'Basque Homeland and Liberty')
title: Euskadi (disambiguation)
